title: Information for Transaero passengers with tickets for 19 October 2015 (Aeroflot OAO)
text: ( Source : Aeroflot OAO ) The following Transaero flights on 19 October 2015 have been cancelled: UN29 St.Petersburg - Vnukovo UN30 Vnukovo - St.Petersburg UN31 St.Petersburg - Domodedovo UN32 Domodedovo - St.Petersburg UN102 Norilsk - Vnukovo
